@startuml
' --- whole-map provenance: cycle that introduced each @id ---
' @cycle(CMP-DEPLOY-SKILL, 0007)
' @cycle(CMP-DEPLOY-STORE, 0007)
' @cycle(CMP-DEPLOY-TARGET, 0007)
' @cycle(CMP-DEPLOY-RENDER, 0007)
' @cycle(CMP-DEPLOY-PROFILE-DOC, 0007)
' @cycle(CMP-DEPLOY-EXEC, 0021)
' @id(CMP-DEPLOY-SKILL)
' @id(CMP-DEPLOY-STORE)
' @id(CMP-DEPLOY-TARGET)
' @id(CMP-DEPLOY-RENDER)
' @id(CMP-DEPLOY-PROFILE-DOC)
' @id(CMP-DEPLOY-EXEC)
' @ref(USE-DEPLOY-GUIDANCE)
' @ref(USE-DEPLOY-INSPECT)
' @ref(USE-DEPLOY-EXECUTE)
'
' Current-side ownership boundaries for /mdd-deploy as implemented.
' Canonical source of truth is crates/mdd-core/src/templates.rs; the
' .claude/.codex SKILL.md mirrors and .mdd/docs/deploy-profile.md are
' materialized by `mdd init` (Project::init_with_conflict_handler).
'
' @desc(CMP-DEPLOY-SKILL, "Implemented: templates::MDD_DEPLOY_SKILL + its SkillTemplate entry in templates::WORKFLOW_SKILLS, materialized into .claude/.codex/skills/mdd-deploy/SKILL.md. It PLANS (diagram + runbook + IaC) and then EXECUTES the runbook to live traffic via CMP-DEPLOY-EXEC; a sibling of /mdd-render, outside the parity gate.")
' @desc(CMP-DEPLOY-STORE, "Specified by templates::MDD_DEPLOY_SKILL: .mdd/deploy/<target>/ (diagram.puml + runbook.md), created on the first /mdd-deploy run. Naturally outside /mdd-validate and /mdd-review scope, like the non-gated .mdd/map/ tree.")
' @desc(CMP-DEPLOY-TARGET, "Specified by templates::MDD_DEPLOY_SKILL: the deployment target repo ../atlas-ate-server, read READ-ONLY for topology + security invariants; generated infra/main.bicep written there at skill-run time.")
' @desc(CMP-DEPLOY-RENDER, "Implemented: step 8 of templates::MDD_RENDER_SKILL instructs /mdd-render to rasterize .mdd/deploy/**/*.puml to .mdd/rendered/deploy/**/*.svg. Additive, non-gating.")
' @desc(CMP-DEPLOY-PROFILE-DOC, "Implemented: .mdd/docs/deploy-profile.md, materialized from templates::deploy_profile_doc (MDD_DEPLOY_PROFILE_DOC) by Project::init_with_conflict_handler. Documents the azure-container-apps deployment-diagram conventions, the invariant checklist, and (cycle 0021) the execution model.")
' @desc(CMP-DEPLOY-EXEC, "Cycle 0021: the execution engine — the skill (agent) invokes Bash to run az / terraform / docker against the LIVE Azure subscription, walking the generated runbook. Manages auth, dry-runs before any apply, runs idempotent steps autonomously, BLOCKS at irreversible steps and at go-live, HALTS on first error. NOT a new mdd CLI verb. Outside the parity gate. Realizes USE-DEPLOY-EXECUTE.")
title /mdd-deploy ownership — plan + execute (current)

actor "Operator" as Op

component "/mdd-deploy\n(skill: plan + executor)" as Skill
component "/mdd-render\n(extended)" as Render
component "execution engine\n(agent -> Bash: az / terraform / docker)" as Exec

folder ".mdd/deploy/azure-container-apps/\ndiagram.puml, runbook.md" as Store
folder "../atlas-ate-server/\ninfra/ (Bicep or Terraform)" as Target
folder ".mdd/rendered/deploy/\n**/*.svg" as Rendered
folder ".mdd/docs/deploy-profile.md" as ProfileDoc
cloud "Azure subscription (LIVE)" as Az

package "canonical source of truth" {
  component "crates/mdd-core/src/templates.rs\nMDD_DEPLOY_SKILL + WORKFLOW_SKILLS\n+ MDD_DEPLOY_PROFILE_DOC" as Templates
}

package "existing gated MDD pipeline\n(unaffected)" {
  component "/mdd-cycle / /mdd-validate /\n/mdd-review (parity gate)" as Gate
}

Op --> Skill : /mdd-deploy <description>
Templates ..> Skill : materialized by `mdd init`
Templates ..> ProfileDoc : materialized by `mdd init`
Skill --> Store : write diagram.puml + runbook.md (plan)
Skill --> Target : generate infra/ (plan)
Skill ..> ProfileDoc : follows conventions
Skill --> Exec : drive execution (walk the runbook)
Exec --> Store : read runbook.md as the execution plan
Exec --> Target : apply infra/ (terraform apply / az deployment)
Exec --> Az : auth, apply, provision secrets, migrate, route traffic
Op ..> Exec : auth handshake + confirm irreversible steps & go-live
Op --> Render : /mdd-render
Render --> Store : read .mdd/deploy/**/*.puml
Render --> Rendered : write .mdd/rendered/deploy/**/*.svg
Gate ..> Store : NEVER reads (outside the gate)

note bottom of Skill
  Plans, then EXECUTES the runbook via CMP-DEPLOY-EXEC.
  Now runs az / terraform / docker (the old "never runs"
  non-goal is retired). Realizes USE-DEPLOY-GUIDANCE +
  USE-DEPLOY-EXECUTE.
end note

note bottom of Gate
  /mdd-deploy is decoupled: no objective<->current
  parity, no security-marker parity. A UML
  deployment diagram has no code-derived
  counterpart, so by design it is not routed into
  the gate.
end note
@enduml
